{"word":"H5087 - נָדַר - nâdar - naw-dar' - Vow","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נָדַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>nâdar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>naw-dar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Vow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பொருத்தனைபண்ணு, பொருத்தனை செலுத்து, நேர்ந்துகொள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to vow, to make a vow; (Qal) to vow a vow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>promise</i> (positively, to do or give something to God): - (make a) vow."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5087 - נָדַר - nâdar - naw-dar'/5087\">H5087</a>, <a href=\"#/H5088 - נֶדֶר - neder - neh'-der/5088\">H5088</a>"}]}